To run the application:

1. Navigate to the project directory in your terminal/command prompt.
2. Install the dependencies by running `pip install -r requirements.txt`.
3. Run the app by executing `python app.py`.
4. Open your web browser and navigate to `http://localhost:5000` to access the homepage.

Note: This is a basic implementation, and you will need to enhance the application to include AI-powered recommendations and other features as per your requirements.